title: All-American Chicken & Roast Pumpkin with Sweet-Heat Sauce & Smokey Pear Slaw
description: When it comes to chicken, we’re always looking for two things: golden crackly skin and juicy, flavourful meat. Enter, these baked chicken breast. They’re all that and then some—the “some” being a sticky BBQ and sriracha glaze that really takes them above and beyond.
